<!--
==========================================
STATION + AMENITY — STATIONARY STOP TEST
==========================================

Synced with stationData.ts:
- Station: EV_Station_Test @ 17.42, 78.338 (100m geofence)
- Charging Bay A center: 17.4201, 78.3377 (polygon)
- Cafe: 17.42027, 78.33825 (20m circle)
- Restroom: 17.41965, 78.3381 (15m circle)

SCENARIO:
1. Drive into station geofence
2. Stop 1 — Charging Bay: COMPLETELY STATIONARY 1.5 min (zero movement)
3. Walk to Cafe
4. Stop 2 — Cafe: COMPLETELY STATIONARY 1.5 min
5. Walk to Restroom
6. Stop 3 — Restroom: COMPLETELY STATIONARY 1.5 min
7. Walk back toward exit, drive out of station geofence

Testing notes (stopTimeout=1 min, heartbeat=30s inside station):
- After ~1 min still at each stop → plugin marks stationary → heartbeat every 30s
- Expect ~1 heartbeat during each 1.5 min stop (first heartbeat ~30s after stationary)

All stationary segments use IDENTICAL lat/lon with advancing timestamps only.
==========================================
-->

<!-- PHASE 1: DRIVE TOWARD STATION (south → north) -->
<wpt lat="17.4177" lon="78.338"><ele>520</ele><time>2024-01-01T10:00:00Z</time></wpt>
